电、燃气的费用信息，提醒你及时缴费，为生活带来便利\n新增在小布建议和流体云上，显示小布记忆中保存的已购电影票，方便核销观影\n新增在小布建议和流体云上，显示小布记忆中保存的已购景点门票，方便刷码入园\n新增在小布建议上，显示小布记忆中保存的酒店订房信息，进行酒店入住提醒\n新增桌面超级小布入口，将桌面分页符全搜入口替换为小布助手，唤醒小布更方便\n\n【开启流畅新境界】\n优化自由浮窗进入、调整位置、切换大小等操作动画，更流畅\n\n【处处有细节，细节有惊喜】\n新增官方浏览器支持部分文档处理工具：文档摘要、文档翻译、转为 PDF、转为 Word、转为 Excel\n新增分屏支持无极调节窗口比例。双应用横屏分屏显示时，拖动分隔条，可自由调整分屏大小\n新增在私密保险箱中可分享图片和视频\n新增在私密保险箱中可自定义图片或视频图集封面\n新增在私密保险箱中可按照时间排序查看图片和视频，查找更方便\n新增在私密保险箱的其他文件分类中可直接添加文件进行加密，操作更方便\n新增融合桌面-小窗支持切换使用经典投屏，导航音乐两不误\n新增当最近任务为堆叠样式时，支持在最近任务界面下滑应用卡片修改应用锁定状态\n优化在文档中一次性添加文件到私密保险箱的数量限制，由 500 个修改为不限制个数\n优化短信删除逻辑，全选删除消息时不需要再进行指纹或密码验证，可直接删除\n优化了车载投屏音乐胶囊的界面布局，可以直接在音乐胶囊上播放、暂停、切换歌曲\n优化时钟相关卡片切换逻辑，跟随系统亮暗色切换\n优化简洁横幅通知功能，横屏时收到通知都将以简洁横幅通知形态显示，减少打扰\n优化简洁通知操作手势，收到简洁横幅通知时也可以下滑通知，以浮窗形式显示通知应用界面\n优化点击简洁横幅菜单按钮后的界面跳转形式，由原来的全屏显示改为浮窗显示，减少打扰\n优化横屏时横幅通知显示位置，减少遮挡，降低打扰\n\n【网络通信】\n新增在无网络情况下，可通过无网畅聊给附近的人发送文字、图片和语音消息，方便与同伴联系（设置-移动网络-无网畅聊）\n\n【系统】\n更新 Android 安全补丁至 2025 年 8 月，提升系统安全性","googlePatchDate":"2025/08/01 00:00:00","type":"normal","versionFilename":"PKG110domestic_11_15.0.0.850CN01_2025080621020154.zip","backVersionLink":"https://gpw13.myoas.com/artifactory/after-sale-local/23series/23851_15.0.2_V/%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/MP6/PKG110domestic_11_15.0.0.850CN01_2025080621020154.zip","filePath":"/dfs/25/09/03/cecbdc3d574b4592a3bd10f55c0f7476.zip","fileName":"PKG110domestic_11_15.0.0.850CN01_2025080621020154.zip","md5":"6364d458d4ce36a6f3fcba096e1c19de","colorOs":"ColorOS 15.0.2","androidVersion":"Android 15","updateDescEnglish":"【Effortless AI at every moment】\nAdds the &quot;Pay bills&quot; widget in Breeno Suggestions. It extracts your utility bills (water, electricity, and gas) from text messages and reminds you to pay them on time.\nBreeno Suggestions and Live Alerts now display movie tickets saved in Breeno Memory, allowing you to quickly present them at the entrance.\nBreeno Suggestions and Live Alerts now display tickets for tourist attractions saved in Breeno Memory, allowing you to quickly present them at the entrance.\nBreeno Suggestions now displays hotel booking information saved in Breeno Memory as check-in reminders.\nReplaces Global Search at the bottom of the Home screen with Breeno for easier access.\n\n【Unlock a new level of seamless experience】\nImproves the animations for opening, repositioning, and resizing a floating window.\n\n【Delight in details】\nBrowser now includes new tools to summarize, translate, and convert documents to PDF, Word, or Excel formats.\nSplit View is no longer restricted to fixed ratios. You can now adjust the ratio as needed. In Split View, when two apps are displayed in landscape, you can now drag the divider to adjust their relative sizes.\nYou can now share images and videos in Private Safe.\nYou can now customize image or video album covers in Private Safe.\nYou can now sort and view images and videos by time in Private Safe.\nYou can now add files directly under the &quot;Other files&quot; category in Private Safe.\nFusion Desktop - Small Window now supports switching to the classic casting mode, allowing for seamless navigation and music playback.\nWhen recent tasks are stacked, you can now modify an app's lock status by swiping down on the app on the recent tasks screen.\nYou can now add an unlimited number of files to Private Safe in Documents at once, instead of the previous limit of 500.\nYou can now select and delete all messages without verifying your fingerprint or password.\nImproves the layout of the music player capsule on the car display. You can now play, pause, and switch songs directly in the music player capsule.\nClock-related widgets now switch between light and dark modes based on system settings.\nAll notifications received in landscape mode are now displayed in a simplified banner format to reduce interruptions.\nYou can now swipe down on a simplified banner notification to display the app in a floating window.\nTapping a button on a simplified banner notification now opens the app in a floating window instead of full screen, reducing interruptions.\nAdjusts the position of banner notifications in landscape mode to minimize distractions.\n\n【Network connections】\nYou can now send text, image, and voice messages to nearby people via BeaconLink when there is no internet connection. You can find this feature in &quot;Settings - Mobile network - BeaconLink&quot;.\n\n【System】\nIntegrates the August 2025 Android security patch to enhance system security.","companyName":null,"fileSize":10776237729,"softwareVersion":"15.0.0.850(CN01)","projectNo":"23851","host":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com","nvFileInfo":[{"nv":"nv_10010111","path":"/dfs/25/09/03/da6a4b114a6f4ee79abd632f1f9c2b98.zip","md5":"37bbc435607dcc572f8d1bbd35f1aab3","size":1872299429,"taskId":"up-id-ebf80376-c0e8-4252-b0f3-78e47b97c921"},{"nv":"common","path":"/dfs/25/09/03/dd45c903b35b444ebc6594020a583674.zip","md5":"49eeecc6951525476dc660fa7fab7967","size":8678013305,"taskId":"up-id-ef279297-6a9f-4ebc-bc28-f1b9c6b540c0"},{"nv":"nv_00000000","path":"/dfs/25/09/03/55109652718c4f0d8dd12234bd9ec75b.zip","md5":"37bbc435607dcc572f8d1bbd35f1aab3","size":1872299429,"taskId":"up-id-cfa652d1-0699-41d4-9dc1-90b17d8e9cbb"}]},{"inSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/07/30/6b7c97c4dc704a429564bffc038633f3.zip","outSalesLink":"https://dfs-serverauto-cn.allawnfs.com/dfs/25/07/30/6b7c97c4dc704a429564bffc038633f3.zip","marketModel":"一加 Ace 5","updateDesc":null,"googlePatchDate":"2025/07/01 00:00:00","type":"normal","versionFilename":"PKG110domestic_11_15.0.0.840CN01_2025070723200186.zip","backVersionLink":"https://gpw13.myoas.com/artifactory/after-sale-local/23series/23851_15.0.2_V/%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC/MP4/PKG110domestic_11_15.0.0.840CN01_2025070723200186.zip","filePath":"/dfs/25/07/30/6b7c97c4dc704a429564bffc038633f3.zip","fileName":"PKG110domestic_11_15.0.0.840CN01_2025070723200186.zip","md5":"3e2e880f569f1075ea166a49c6e89588","colorOs":"ColorOS 15.0.2","androidVersion":"Android 15","updateDescEnglish":nul